##nome:
webhook-cancelar

##descricao:
Webhook enviada pela vindi no momento do cancelamento

##outras-urls:
http://localhost/api/webhook/vindi
https://gateway.unimestre.com/api/webhook/vindi

##url:
http://localhost/api/webhook/vindi

##metodo:
post

##headers:
Content-Type:application/json

